                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">WoW sounds pretty good, but I haven't seen answers to some questions I have.
<br />

<br />
How many characters can you have per account? How big is your inventory? Do you have bags? How much can the bank hold? Where are the banks? Can items be transfered between characters on the same account (assuming more than one)? Does there look to be a user economy? How is death handled? A corpse run? What is the death penalty? (I assume there's gotta be some kind of penalty) How is PvP handled? (no, I do NOT want to PvP - which is why I ask) Do they expect to have multiple servers? How big do they expect server population to be? How is LFG handled? There were two 'names' enclosed by &lt;...&gt; on one of the screenshots. One was the guild name, what was the other?
<br />

<br />
I'm sure there's some more trivial questions I've missed <img src="images/smiles/icon_wink.gif" alt="icon_wink.gif" border="0" /></span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Max
